819
00:53:37,771 --> 00:53:39,321
just like you.

820
00:53:39,501 --> 00:53:40,662
What? "Lame"?

821
00:53:40,911 --> 00:53:42,442
Are you seriously going to blame it on me?

822
00:53:42,442 --> 00:53:44,231
We'll soon find out.

823
00:53:44,581 --> 00:53:46,411
You just wait and see.

824
00:53:46,411 --> 00:53:48,982
We'll end up going to a bed and breakfast...

825
00:53:48,982 --> 00:53:50,702
that's run by an old lady.

826
00:53:52,922 --> 00:53:54,692
(Bed and Breakfast)

827
00:53:54,692 --> 00:53:56,001
Hello?

828
00:53:57,621 --> 00:53:58,812
Is anyone here?

829
00:53:59,762 --> 00:54:02,362
