884
00:57:58,061 --> 00:57:59,952
We have a stove.

885
00:58:01,771 --> 00:58:05,222
It's an induction stove. Is that why you couldn't find it?

886
00:58:06,902 --> 00:58:08,521
We saw an iron cauldron.

887
00:58:09,471 --> 00:58:11,162
I put that there to make the place look nice.

888
00:58:16,052 --> 00:58:17,671
Did you cook rice?

889
00:58:17,851 --> 00:58:19,771
We provide meals for our guests.

890
00:58:19,951 --> 00:58:22,602
We bring it all the way to your room like a hotel room service.

891
00:58:24,061 --> 00:58:27,282
You guys are very old-fashioned.

892
00:58:36,001 --> 00:58:37,651
It's nice and warm.

893
00:58:39,302 --> 00:58:41,662
Here's your coffee.

894
00:58:42,271 --> 00:58:43,622
- Thank you. - No problem.

895
00:58:44,982 --> 00:58:46,532
I've never had coffee in a bowl.

896
00:58:47,311 --> 00:58:48,602
Bowl coffee.

897
00:58:52,751 --> 00:58:56,571
I Sang, how did you end up doing photography?

898
00:58:57,462 --> 00:59:00,841
My dad used to enjoy taking photos.

899
00:59:01,232 --> 00:59:02,931
I used to follow my dad to the photo studio...

900
00:59:02,931 --> 00:59:04,682
every time he went there to get his photos printed out.

901
00:59:05,032 --> 00:59:07,211
Then I'd follow him again once the photos were ready.

902
00:59:07,732 --> 00:59:09,421
I enjoyed doing that.

903
00:59:11,041 --> 00:59:13,591
I guess that's why your photos are always so warm.

904
00:59:18,411 --> 00:59:20,432
Your photos are just like you.

905
00:59:24,822 --> 00:59:27,552
Back in the past, we had to wait...

906
00:59:27,552 --> 00:59:29,202
until the photos came out.

907
00:59:30,052 --> 00:59:32,642
It was exciting to wait for them.

908
00:59:33,521 --> 00:59:35,881
It's just like how I can't wait to find out...

909
00:59:36,262 --> 00:59:38,082
what will happen tomorrow.

910
00:59:41,132 --> 00:59:43,321
I'm more curious about today.

911
00:59:46,201 --> 00:59:49,662
I wonder how we'll end up spending the night together.

912
01:00:18,971 --> 01:00:20,421
It's good, right?

913
01:00:33,021 --> 01:00:34,841
- Are you done washing up? - Yes.

914
01:00:34,951 --> 01:00:37,042
Well, I was just about to wash up myself.

915
01:00:37,661 --> 01:00:38,711
I see.

916
01:00:40,322 --> 01:00:42,312
Do they have hot water?

917
01:00:42,632 --> 01:00:44,282
Yes, lots of it.

918
01:00:45,431 --> 01:00:47,952
Right. Good night then.

919
01:00:49,101 --> 01:00:51,292
- Good night. - You too.

