01:04:33,962 --> 01:04:35,111
Just a second.

926
01:04:37,462 --> 01:04:40,012
Why are you whispering?

927
01:04:52,811 --> 01:04:53,961
Wait.

928
01:05:07,632 --> 01:05:08,782
This looks so cool.

929
01:05:30,581 --> 01:05:32,301
Gosh, the wind.

930
01:05:34,592 --> 01:05:36,142
My hair's all over the place.

931
01:05:40,661 --> 01:05:42,912
- What a windy day. - What?

932
01:05:50,632 --> 01:05:54,091
Being a big guy, I'm sure you can block the wind for me...

